name: Astro Globes: Solar Prominence
description:
Astro Globes is a series of uniquely processed astrophotography from my own collection with each image featuring a different object in our skies. 
This incredible inverted image of our Sun features a large Solar Prominence erupting on the outer limb as well as a sunspot. It was taken using a telescope with a specialised Hydrogen Alpha wavelength filter, please do not look at the sun without the appropriate filters.
